{"tid":320821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大海發現大象！ 斯里蘭卡海軍助牠奇蹟脫逃","createTime":"2017-07-13T19:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T06:47:45.000Z","uid":78764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39b9211d7ddf216b1820898d7542d55a64d343a8","tid":320821,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:52:37.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕斯里蘭卡海軍日前在東北沿海巡航時，在離岸約8公里的海上發現1隻差點溺水的大象。軍方花了12小時營救，最後成功將牠救上岸。參與營救行動的人員直呼，這隻大象簡直是「奇蹟脫逃」！<br />\n綜合外電報導，斯里蘭卡海軍1艘巡航艦在東北沿海約8公里處海域，發現1隻載浮載沉的大象，努力將象鼻伸出海面。海軍隨後與野生動物管理部門合作，派出潛水員在牠身上綁上繩索後，用另1艘軍艦把牠拖回岸邊，最後共花了12小時才將大象救上岸。<br />\n海軍發言人瓦拉庫魯治（Chaminda Walakuluge）表示，大象常為了「抄捷徑」游過森林間的潟湖，估計牠可能在途中不小心被捲入海流，才會游到海上卻差點滅頂。對於這次營救成功，瓦拉庫魯治也驚呼這是大象的「奇蹟脫逃」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O5WcE6OwkBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO5WcE6OwkBw&d=krhCVuX83pwQhsfRk3zr5MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=45485d0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O5WcE6OwkBw</a>"},{"pid":"c00ddc0916bb976228a4d28b9c9411c43a75097d","tid":320821,"uid":78764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:53:10.000Z","msg":"到底佢游左幾耐水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c985a81b039439b0f4bef1c54c628c67d64571ee","tid":320821,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:57:27.000Z","msg":"識游水咁叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01bcf87d731d2aa48a2bc89b7b1d424cf58b5a2","tid":320821,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底佢游左幾耐水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到底邊個仆街非法販賣動物就真。"},{"pid":"72112093233b08ccc28dee552844d73460788f2d","tid":320821,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:58:56.000Z","msg":"新聞有播，睇完心upup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩最後無事 <img src=\"/a